Detailed Description

Structure representing an individual timer.

Each timer has a timer period, a memory management pool, and a list of buckets.

This is the structure passed to the kernel. It must be kept in sync with cvmx_tim_t in this file and in linux/arch/mips/cavium-octeon/cavium.c.

Internal use function. This function's parameters and processing may change in future SDKs.
